        "content": "<p>Which among the two designs you folks like more?</p>\n<p><strong> Square User Avatar in User Info Popup</strong></p>\n<ul>\n<li><a href=\"/user_uploads/2/50/PcR0i4m3J4cGGIYaWhFcnGHF/Screenshot-from-2017-03-05-232457.png\" target=\"_blank\" title=\"Screenshot-from-2017-03-05-232457.png\">Square-Avatar-Example-A.png</a></li>\n<li><a href=\"/user_uploads/2/61/qJRrN6tQGItFEiMJqCo7kUWe/Screenshot-from-2017-03-05-232019.png\" target=\"_blank\" title=\"Screenshot-from-2017-03-05-232019.png\">Square-Avatar-Example-B.png</a> </li>\n</ul>\n<p><strong>Rectangle User Avatar in User Info Popup</strong></p>\n<ul>\n<li><a href=\"/user_uploads/2/12/jzHkUrHfzxEW9hzLDOUfMBDi/Screenshot-from-2017-03-05-224024.png\" target=\"_blank\" title=\"Screenshot-from-2017-03-05-224024.png\">Rectangle-Avatar-Example-A.png</a> </li>\n<li><a href=\"https://chat.zulip.org/user_uploads/2/93/WgMEGRSbmA2vXVHGiDTEf81a/Screenshot-from-2017-03-05-232435.png\" target=\"_blank\" title=\"Screenshot-from-2017-03-05-232435.png\">Rectangle-Avatar-Example-B.png</a></li>\n</ul>\n<p>The drawback of having rectangle user avatar box is that it cutoffs portion from top and bottom(equally) from the default user avatars in Zulip which are square in shape.</p>\n<div class=\"message_inline_image\"><a href=\"https://chat.zulip.org/user_uploads/2/93/WgMEGRSbmA2vXVHGiDTEf81a/Screenshot-from-2017-03-05-232435.png\" target=\"_blank\" title=\"Rectangle-Avatar-Example-B.png\"><img src=\"https://chat.zulip.org/user_uploads/2/93/WgMEGRSbmA2vXVHGiDTEf81a/Screenshot-from-2017-03-05-232435.png\"></a></div><div class=\"message_inline_image\"><a href=\"/user_uploads/2/12/jzHkUrHfzxEW9hzLDOUfMBDi/Screenshot-from-2017-03-05-224024.png\" target=\"_blank\" title=\"Rectangle-Avatar-Example-A.png\"><img src=\"/user_uploads/2/12/jzHkUrHfzxEW9hzLDOUfMBDi/Screenshot-from-2017-03-05-224024.png\"></a></div><div class=\"message_inline_image\"><a href=\"/user_uploads/2/61/qJRrN6tQGItFEiMJqCo7kUWe/Screenshot-from-2017-03-05-232019.png\" target=\"_blank\" title=\"Square-Avatar-Example-B.png\"><img src=\"/user_uploads/2/61/qJRrN6tQGItFEiMJqCo7kUWe/Screenshot-from-2017-03-05-232019.png\"></a></div><div class=\"message_inline_image\"><a href=\"/user_uploads/2/50/PcR0i4m3J4cGGIYaWhFcnGHF/Screenshot-from-2017-03-05-232457.png\" target=\"_blank\" title=\"Square-Avatar-Example-A.png\"><img src=\"/user_uploads/2/50/PcR0i4m3J4cGGIYaWhFcnGHF/Screenshot-from-2017-03-05-232457.png\"></a></div>",
