        "content": "<p>what would you think of not show the image if it is a gravitar?</p>",
        "id": 163322,
        "sender_full_name": "Rishi Gupta",
        "timestamp": 1488830093
    },
    {
        "content": "<p>Inconsistency isn't great; I think this will make avatars more prominent and thus push people towards using them</p>",
        "id": 163324,
        "sender_full_name": "Tim Abbott",
        "timestamp": 1488830367
    },
    {
        "content": "<p>Yeah, I would have just said the same. Show it always.<br>\nOn the other hand, these default gravatars don't look appropriate for a chat really, more for a potentially anonymous commenting on the Internet.</p>",
        "id": 163325,
        "sender_full_name": "Boris Yankov",
        "timestamp": 1488830445
    },
    {
        "content": "<p>Maybe have a default 'faceless head' ala the Twitter egg kinda thing.</p>",
        "id": 163326,
        "sender_full_name": "Boris Yankov",
        "timestamp": 1488830491
    },
    {
        "content": "<p>I like how my SMS app does it - a colored circle with the person's initials</p>",
