        "id": 163328,
        "sender_full_name": "Sumana Harihareswara",
        "timestamp": 1488830543
    },
    {
        "content": "<p>Oh, yeah, we do that in the mobile app actually</p>",
        "id": 163329,
        "sender_full_name": "Boris Yankov",
        "timestamp": 1488830557
    },
    {
        "content": "<p>This is how we do it in the mobile app:<br>\n<a href=\"https://github.com/zulip/zulip-mobile/blob/master/src/common/TextAvatar.js#L7\" target=\"_blank\" title=\"https://github.com/zulip/zulip-mobile/blob/master/src/common/TextAvatar.js#L7\">https://github.com/zulip/zulip-mobile/blob/master/src/common/TextAvatar.js#L7</a></p>",
        "id": 163332,
        "sender_full_name": "Boris Yankov",
        "timestamp": 1488830625
    },
    {
        "content": "<p><code>colorHashFromName</code> ensures the same name produces the same color always</p>",
        "id": 163333,
        "sender_full_name": "Boris Yankov",
        "timestamp": 1488830654
    },
    {
        "content": "<p>I guess it might be better to key off <code>user_id</code> so that it doesn't change if you change your name.<br>\nBut yeah, we've talked about stopping using gravatar for the default system avatars</p>",
        "id": 163334,
        "sender_full_name": "Tim Abbott",
        "timestamp": 1488830742
